Class MockFilterRegistration

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    javax.servlet.FilterConfig, javax.servlet.FilterRegistration, javax.servlet.FilterRegistration.Dynamic, javax.servlet.Registration, javax.servlet.Registration.Dynamic

    public class MockFilterRegistration
extends AbstractMockRegistration
implements javax.servlet.FilterRegistration.Dynamic, javax.servlet.FilterConfig
    Mock version of a FilterRegistration.Dynamic that does nothing but keep a number of configured properties. Support is limited and only intended in combination with MockAcrossServletContext.
    Author:
    Marc Vanbrabant, Arne Vandamme
